

machine
	all the hardware used to operate the add-on card. Typically this
	includes CPU, motherboard (PCI) chipset, etc.

system
	The software environment we have to run/compile under. Mainly this 
	will include compilers, assemblers, linkers, operating systems,...

workplace
	A set of output devices (displays) and input devices operated
	by one user. A user is not allowed to use input and output 
	resources that do not belong to his/her workplace.

